% Use Erlang's own DNS resolver (inet_res) pointed at Docker's embedded DNS.
% Alpine musl's native resolver fails on .local Docker aliases; inet_res works fine.
% Docker DNS (127.0.0.11) resolves network aliases and returns NOERROR for SRV
% queries so ejabberd S2S falls back to A-record lookup correctly.
{nameserver, {127,0,0,11}}.
{lookup, [dns]}.
